4205623.name: 6788 (Stella York)
4205623.notes: Exquisitely boho and perfectly casual, this wedding dress by bridal designer Stella York is a dreamy combination of comfort and style. Lace and delicate French tulle create a relaxed A-line silhouette made for magical moments. This dress is definitely for the fashion-forward boho bride with its really cool triangle back detail. Swiss dots are used on the bodice throughout the lace, making the pattern of the boho lace interesting and unique. A hint of twinkle has also been added to the lace to juxtapose the softness of the French tulle skirt. The triangle back is the real showpiece of this dress. Made of beaded shoestring straps, the geometric back demands to be seen.

4773028.notes: This modern wedding gown with dreamlike elements is something of another world! French lace brings the romance with this mixed-material bridal dress from Essense of Australia, placed atop tulle and embroidered laces to create the slightly sheer bodice with elegant high neckline and striking centerfront plunge. The beaded shoestring straps extend into a geometric, multi-banded back detail that is the epitome of fashion-forward style. Laces then trickle over strong, angular side cutouts for a stunning figure-falling onto the smooth stretch crepe for a negative space element. The dress transitions once again from the crepe skirt to the lace and tulle train, with unexpected scalloping and an out-of-this-world finish.

4816073.notes: Modern boho brides, take note, this sexy lace wedding dress from Essense of Australia was made for you! This mix of French lace and cotton lace continues down through the sheer bodice, adding the perfect amount of sexiness to the style. From the bodice, the scrolling lace pattern continues down through the slight fit-and-flare silhouette, highlighted with latticework that makes it truly unique. Layers upon layers of tulle make the skirt of this gown appear light as air, and completely boho. The back of this wedding dress is highlighted with a scoop back, complete with organic lace trim. Illusion tulle gives a peek-a-boo look that extends into sexy sheer side cutouts. The back of this gown zips up beneath fabric-covered buttons.
